ice.</string><string name="celebration_cta">Continue</string><string name="celebration_journey_done">You\'ve completed the journey 🌱</string><string name="reaffirmation_share">Share this reaffirmation</string><string name="journey_stat_streak">day streak</string><string name="journey_stat_completed">completed</string><string name="onboarding_stages_cta">Continue</string><string name="onboarding_intro_title">Hi — I\'m Ori</string><string name="onboarding_promises_3">Write the true thing, not the impressive thing. No one is grading this.</string><string name="onboarding_promises_cta">I promise</string><string name="onboarding_day_evening">An evening reflection to close the day</string><string name="onboarding_promises_1">There\'s no perfect way to do this.</string><string name="onboarding_promises_2">Missing a day isn\'t failing — it\'s being a person. Come back when you can; the page will wait.</string><string name="onboarding_respond_numb">Numb is its own kind of weather, %s. We\'ll start gently, and you don\'t have to feel everything at once. Showing up is the whole task today.</string><string name="onboarding_feeling_peace">At peace with myself</string><string name="onboarding_mood_heavy">Heavy</string><string name="onboarding_mood_tired">Tired</string><string name="onboarding_stage_connector_peace">Then we\'ll spend real time in Self-Acceptance — it\'s where this whole journey begins, and where peace finds its footing.</string><string name="onboarding_stage_connector_clear">Then Purpose is where this is headed — turning everything you uncover into a direction worth walking.</string><string name="onboarding_feeling_connected">Connected</string><string name="onboarding_day_action">A mindful action, under fifteen minutes</string><string name="onboarding_stage_connector_confident">Then Empowerment is going to matter to you — learning to trust and back yourself, a little more each day.</string><string name="onboarding_respond_tired">Tired is allowed here, %s. We\'ll g